static void insertQuery::main ( String[]  Args  )  [inline, static]

Inserts the given query. Each space character is considered as a new argument to the program. There are three spaces in the program which is calling this program. (Insert into xxx(a,b,c...) values....) All 4 words are reconnected before inserting a new record.
